01:10:08.160 --> 01:10:11.160
We want a simple label we can point to so we can rest.

01:10:11.720 --> 01:10:16.360
But the math shows us that your identity isn't that frozen static snapshot.

01:10:16.800 --> 01:10:23.240
It's the living, breathing, irreversible log of how you heal, how you change, and where you

01:10:23.240 --> 01:10:24.840
boldly choose to walk next.

01:10:25.020 --> 01:10:28.340
It is the entirety of your history and the horizon of your future.

01:10:28.340 --> 01:10:33.060
So I want to leave you with one final lingering question to mull over as you go about the

01:10:33.060 --> 01:10:33.680
rest of your day.

01:10:34.300 --> 01:10:40.520
If your identity is essentially a sovereign, append-only log, and every unconstrained shortcut

01:10:40.520 --> 01:10:45.680
you take is permanently, irreversibly compiled into the foundation of your trajectory, what

01:10:45.680 --> 01:10:50.860
invisible permanent code are you writing into yourself right now, simply by which you choose

